rows.label: qst200501_0010
rows.name:
...What do you intend
to do with that fire?

rows.label: qst200501_0030
rows.name:
Could you put the things you've
gathered into the fire?

rows.label: qst200501_0040
rows.name:
We went to all the trouble of gathering them,
and now we're just going to burn them?

rows.label: qst200501_0070
rows.name:
Diblo have a habit of
liking a particular smell.

rows.label: qst200501_0080
rows.name:
If we use that well, we
can guide them over here.

rows.label: qst200501_0100
rows.name:
So the things we gathered earlier
were to produce that smell.

rows.label: qst200501_0110
rows.name:
If this smell wafts over to the
Diblo, they will approach this area.

rows.label: qst200501_0120
rows.name:
If this goes well, we should be able to
retrieve the cargo without fighting.

rows.label: qst200501_0130
rows.name: Will this really gather them all, mo?

rows.label: qst200501_0150
rows.name:
Now, let's move a little
and watch from a distance.

rows.label: qst200501_0170
rows.name:
It may not be all of them, but... this
should make the retrieval a bit easier.

rows.label: qst200501_0180
rows.name: Amazing, mo! Yuou is very reliable, mo.

rows.label: qst200501_0190
rows.name:
Thank you. But I merely
did what was natural.
